					</h2>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">By use case</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Jump to detailed comparisons for your specific use case:</p>
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6">
						<a href="/best-ai-website-builder-for-portfolio" class="block group">
							<div class="bg-white p-4 border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20 hover:border-[#F5521A] hover:shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgba(245,82,26,0.2)] transition-all duration-300">
								<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
									<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#F5521A]"></div>
									<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Portfolio:</strong> Framer AI →</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</a>
						<a href="/ai-website-builder-for-ecommerce" class="block group">
