								<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
									<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-600"></div>
									<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Blog:</strong> 10Web AI (WordPress) →</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</a>
						<a href="/best-ai-website-builder-free-no-credit-card" class="block group md:col-span-2">
							<div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 border-[3px] border-blue-200 hover:border-blue-600 hover:shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgba(59,130,246,0.2)] transition-all duration-300">
								<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
									<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></div>
									<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Free trials:</strong> No credit card required →</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</a>
					</div>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">By budget</h3>
					<div class="my-6">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 pb-3">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
							<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Free:</strong> Relume AI (up to 3 projects)</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 pb-3">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
							<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Under $15/mo:</strong> Durable AI ($12/mo)</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
							<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>$15-25/mo:</strong> Framer AI, 10Web AI</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">By skill level</h3>
					<div class="my-6">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 pb-3">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
							<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Beginner:</strong> Durable AI (simplest)</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3 pb-3">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
							<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Intermediate:</strong> Framer AI</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
							<div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
							<span class="text-gray-900"><strong>Advanced:</strong> 10Web AI (requires WordPress knowledge), Relume AI (requires Figma/Webflow)</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
						<div class="w-1 h-8 bg-[#F5521A]"></div>
						The truth about AI website builders
					</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						None of these tools are perfect. All have:
					</p>
					<ul class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						<li><strong>Vendor lock-in:</strong> You can't easily leave (except 10Web/WordPress)</li>
						<li><strong>Limited customization:</strong> You're working within their templates</li>
						<li><strong>Recurring costs:</strong> You pay monthly forever or lose your site</li>
						<li><strong>AI limitations:</strong> The AI gets you 80% there, you do the last 20%</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
